{"word":"H3957 - לִשְׁכָּה - lishkâh - lish-kaw' - Chamber","slug":"H3957","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">לִשְׁכָּה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>lishkâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>lish-kaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Chamber"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DC;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DB;&#x05BC;&#x05D4; - lishka&#x0302;h</b> - <i>lish-kaw'</i><p/>From an unused root of uncertain meaning; a <i>room</i> in a building (whether for storage, eating, or lodging): - chamber, parlour. Compare <a href=\"#/H5393\">H5393</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3958\">H3958</a>, <a href=\"#/H3959\">H3959</a>"}]}